00:17:01.743 --> 00:17:04.147
Really? I'm good, honest.

00:17:04.247 --> 00:17:06.451
Hey, let's go to
karaoke, Yamato!

00:17:06.553 --> 00:17:08.590
You remember you said
you were going.

