Hang on just a second.

00:19:08.663 --> 00:19:09.799
[Girl] Who is it?

00:19:11.969 --> 00:19:13.707
Hello?

00:19:13.807 --> 00:19:15.744
[Mei] Um...

00:19:15.844 --> 00:19:18.182
This is Tachibana.

00:19:18.282 --> 00:19:19.819
I... I need your help!

00:19:19.919 --> 00:19:22.524
[Yamato] It's okay, Mei.
Just tell me where you are.

00:19:22.624 --> 00:19:24.528
[Mei] The convenience
store on Third.

00:19:24.628 --> 00:19:26.766
[Yamato] Stay put, I'm coming!

00:19:26.866 --> 00:19:27.935
[Mei] Okay.

00:19:33.780 --> 00:19:34.347
What's wrong?

00:19:34.447 --> 00:19:35.349
It's that creepy guy

00:19:35.449 --> 00:19:36.652
standing outside the store.

00:19:36.753 --> 00:19:38.590
