the bakery where I work,

00:19:38.690 --> 00:19:42.831
everday, he followed me
tonight and now he's just
standing there!

00:19:42.931 --> 00:19:44.434
I'm scared!

00:19:44.535 --> 00:19:46.271
How long have you been
in the store?

00:19:46.371 --> 00:19:48.175
[Mei] About 35 minutes.

00:19:48.275 --> 00:19:50.714
That's not good! The guy
really is stalking you!

00:19:50.814 --> 00:19:53.553
I-I don't know what I'm
gonna do Kurosawa.

00:19:53.653 --> 00:19:55.089
My mom wasn't picking
up her phone,

00:19:55.189 --> 00:19:56.491
and I didn't know who
else to call!

00:19:56.592 --> 00:19:58.095
[register ringing
up Yamato's goods]

00:19:58.195 --> 00:19:59.899
[Clerk] Thank you very much.

00:19:59.999 --> 00:20:01.703
Um, Kurosawa?

00:20:01.803 --> 00:20:03.138
[Yamato] Here.

00:20:03.238 --> 00:20:04.875
[Mei] Ice cream?

00:20:04.975 --> 00:20:06.713
[Yamato] I got hot running here.

