00:20:10.721 --> 00:20:11.689
All right. Let's go!

00:20:11.789 --> 00:20:13.793
Uh... H-Hey!

00:20:23.045 --> 00:20:24.380
[Yamato] It's okay, Mei.

00:20:28.656 --> 00:20:29.792
Wait a minute.

00:20:31.228 --> 00:20:32.765
[Salary man] Who's he?

00:20:32.865 --> 00:20:34.000
Your boyfriend?

00:20:36.304 --> 00:20:37.574
[Yamato] Mei.

00:20:40.179 --> 00:20:41.481
I love you.

00:20:41.582 --> 00:20:42.718
Huh?

00:21:26.839 --> 00:21:28.408
<i>[Mei] He kissed me.</i>

00:21:30.514 --> 00:21:33.385
<i>What's going to happen</i>
<i>to me now?</i>

00:21:36.024 --> 00:21:37.628
He's gone now.

00:21:38.863 --> 00:21:39.999
Uh, Mei?

00:21:41.101 --> 00:21:45.042
<i>[Mei] And that was</i>
<i>the place, I had my first...</i>

00:21:53.192 --> 00:21:54.628
<i>My first...</i>

00:21:56.431 --> 00:21:57.801
<i>...kiss.</i>

