So this is "Say 'I Love You,'"

00:23:35.830 --> 00:23:38.235
and these are our first steps.

00:23:38.335 --> 00:23:42.209
When you're in a rush, you can
always just call it "Love Ya."

00:23:42.310 --> 00:23:44.815
[Mashmallow] That's
pushing it, meow.

